==German==
===Etymology===
Old High German ''[[klīban]]''
===Transitive verb===
'''kleben''' (past ''klebte'', p.p. ''geklebt'')

# to [[glue]] (onto). Used with preposition [[an]] and [[accusative case]].

===Intransitive verb===
'''kleben'''

# to [[stick]] (to). Used with preposition [[an]] and [[dative case]].
# to be [[sticky]].

===Derived words===
* [[zusammenkleben]]
* [[Klebe]]
* [[Klebeband]]

